window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Bond a dragon. Slay behemoths. Level up or die in a brutal monster-hunting world where every skill-tree decision has teeth.</p> <p>Rohgar has one way off the bottom of the food chain: bond with a hatchling sky-dragon and carve a path through behemoth-infested wilds.</p> <p>In the primal LitRPG world of Aluria, hunters live and die by cultivation stats, evolving weapon styles, and the ruthless logic of the System. Rohgar’s dragon link grants unheard-of synergy skills—fire-laced claw combos, shared XP, and airborne traversal—but it also paints a target on his back. When a necromancer unleashes undead leviathans to harvest the planet’s core essence, Rohgar must speed-run from weak-to-legendary before the kill-clock hits zero.</p> <p>Inside you’ll get</p> <p>• Dragon-bond progression—think The Primal Hunter meets How to Train Your Dragon</p> <p>• Boss-scale behemoth battles and crafting-tree min-maxing</p> <p>• A relentless weak-to-strong climb, zero harem, all action</p> <p>• Perfect for fans of We Hunt Monsters, World According to Dragons, and He Who Fights with Monsters</p> <p>Ready to unleash your primal power? Press play and level up today.</p>"; 
